## Background and Motivation

When hub contracts are defined by interfaces, it is useful to have methods with a `CancellationToken` parameter.

## Proposed API

Similar to controllers and minimal APIs, if a method parameter is of type `CancellationToken`, `Hub.Context.ConnectionAborted` is passed.

